item.title: CVE-2024-37889|2024-06-14T19:12:14.977Z -- treyww -- myfinances
item.description: MyFinances is a web application for managing finances. MyFinances has a way to access other customer invoices while signed in as a user. This method allows an actor to access PII and financial information from another account. The vulnerability is fixed in 0.4.6.
